---
title: "Dynamic: Generate Report"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Organization Admin
    participant UI as UI Components
    participant DataSvc as AccessIntelligenceDataService
    participant GenSvc as ReportGenerationService
    participant HealthSvc as CipherHealthService
    participant MapSvc as MemberCipherMappingService
    participant PersistSvc as ReportPersistenceService
    participant Server as Bitwarden Server

    Admin->>UI: clicks "Generate Report"
    UI->>DataSvc: generateNewReport$(orgId)
    Note over DataSvc: loading$ = true

    par Fetch org data in parallel
        DataSvc->>Server: fetch CipherView[]
        DataSvc->>Server: fetch OrganizationUserView[]
        DataSvc->>Server: fetch GroupMembershipDetails[]
        DataSvc->>Server: fetch CollectionAccessDetails[]
        DataSvc->>Server: loadReport$(orgId) — previous app settings
    end
    Server-->>DataSvc: org data + previous ApplicationHealthView[]

    DataSvc->>GenSvc: generateReport(ciphers, members, collections, groups, previousApps)

    par Run health + mapping in parallel
        GenSvc->>HealthSvc: checkCipherHealth(ciphers)
        Note over HealthSvc: detectPasswordReuse(ciphers)<br/>checkExposedPasswords(ciphers)<br/>via Have I Been Pwned
        HealthSvc-->>GenSvc: Map~CipherId, CipherHealthView~

        GenSvc->>MapSvc: mapCiphersToMembers(ciphers, members, collections, groups)
        MapSvc-->>GenSvc: MemberCipherMappingResult
    end

    GenSvc->>GenSvc: aggregate health + mapping into ApplicationHealthView[]
    GenSvc->>GenSvc: carry over previous critical flags + review dates
    GenSvc->>GenSvc: compute AccessReportSummaryView
    GenSvc-->>DataSvc: AccessReportView

    DataSvc-->>UI: report$ emits AccessReportView
    Note over UI: loading$ = false<br/>UI updates with new report

    DataSvc->>PersistSvc: saveReport$(view, orgId) [async, background]
    Note over PersistSvc: encrypt + version report payload<br/>save metadata + summary to DB<br/>upload payload to blob storage (planned)
    PersistSvc->>Server: save metadata + summary (RiskInsightsApiService)
    PersistSvc->>Server: upload encrypted payload (ReportStorageApiService — planned)
